headline: McCormick Announces Kasey Jenkins' Plan to Retire
summary: McCormick & Company, Incorporated (NYSE: MKC), a global leader in flavor, today announced that Kasey Jenkins, Chief Growth Officer, will retire in early 2026. Over the balance of 2025, Ms. Jenkins will transition her responsibilities to several of the Company's senior leaders.
